{"tid":1941368,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京奧運聖火取消火炬手接力！","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T11:26:37.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59060c38cbda39dd14f27d91683b983821425d00","tid":1941368,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b349ba034c7fc840c902cd2fb889a94288ce935f","tid":1941368,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"東京奧運聖火傳遞將會取消火炬手接力。<br />\n<br />\n東京奧運聖火原定周四，在311地震重災區福島縣展開為期121日的接力傳遞。福島縣官員表示，聖火傳遞的規模將會縮小，不會讓火炬手參與，聖火會放在火種盒。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，東京奧組委考慮由車輛運送火種盒，取代以往透過多名火炬手一人傳一人接力。東京奧組委秘書長武藤敏郎預料稍後會公布詳情。有火炬手表示並未收到任何通知聖火傳遞會有變動。<br />\n<br />\n聖火傳遞原定有大約1萬名火炬手，但日本女足國腳川澄奈穗美早前已經宣布退出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=385525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385525&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ4GpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=3a5f230b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385525&h=ddec7a17\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=385525</a>"},{"pid":"b532931e6257dbcd0454c18ddba8590744eebdf1","tid":1941368,"uid":345137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"去邊都隔離14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}